      • qualifyType

        public static String qualifyType(com.sun.tools.javac.tree.TreeMaker make,
                                 SuggestedFix.Builder fix,
                                 com.sun.tools.javac.code.Symbol.TypeSymbol sym)
        Returns a human-friendly name of the given Symbol.TypeSymbol for use in fixes.
        • If the type is already imported, its simple name is used.
        • If an enclosing type is imported, that enclosing type is used as a qualified.
        • Otherwise the outermost enclosing type is imported and used as a qualifier.
